Singapore Shapeways Meetup
events.description: Once again in conjunction with the Singapore 3D Printing Meetup, we welcome all to the the Singapore Shapeways Meetup! For this meetup, on top of the assortment of 3d printed pieces we have in many of the ranges of materials and also some special pieces in Black Arcylate, which was a newly launched material from Shapeways! Also, the meetup will be a somewhat special one being just before the Singapore Maker Faire (25-26 Jun) one! And so, we will also have some folks from the Singapore Science Centre (organizers of the Singapore Maker Faire) to come and share what you can expect from that crazy maker weekend! Also,Â  when you're here with us, do go crazy snapping pics of the stuff! Do also share photos on Instagram, Twitter, etc, tagging Shapeways using @Shapeways or #Shapeways! Cheers and see you all! =D
events.location: Funbie Studios, Funan DigitaLife Mall, Singapore
